{"tid":406062,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新仔又點?新仔唔使識做野?","createTime":"2017-09-19T10:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T11:40:33.000Z","uid":78457,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8be18110f4e5250db668e3f5a6a6d7aa6c2334e0","tid":406062,"uid":78457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"你又唔教我做<br />\n就係識dum成份野叫我自己睇<br />\n大佬你估份野係說明書咩<br />\n好啦算啦我自學喇<br />\n屌你又唔比時間我學<br />\n第一次接觸就想我做到好似老手咁<br />\n我都明係你個角度嚟講係想我快d上手<br />\n我自問算聽話聽教 同事都覺得我好學<br />\n但你又唔教 又想我做得好?<br />\n唔講咁多 我都係返出去做野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6458f8935e48a9cb6d87c276dc842e5753e30b32","tid":406062,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"腦細 : 番工唔係比你學野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你應該要係空餘時間增值自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b6de3b4984d7194b47f3b408856ee7d38bf98d","tid":406062,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"返工唔同返學<br />\n<br />\n無人教/唔識做 並唔係交唔到貨既原因"},{"pid":"2cdaab753366148a94845cbd81a99a9bbfe8be9a","tid":406062,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8982ec53f0b37514225f9c850b101c42e6571d4d","tid":406062,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"廢就廢啦"},{"pid":"58c7b4ead22b65ef3c15dd7e997caeb39770eb0c","tid":406062,"uid":128928,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"我真金白銀用錢請你返黎學野架?<br />\n你要學就係學校度學哂佢，唔好出黎係獻世<br />\n<br />\n以上既野我都聽過，記到而家"},{"pid":"d24373505692854e581f69e5b645a1587844938d","tid":406062,"uid":78457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工唔同返學<br />\n<br />\n無人教/唔識做 並唔係交唔到貨既原因</blockquote><br />\n我明<br />\n但應該點先可以係